AUDIO: 'restrictions. So, first of all, note that Gemma 4 comes in four sizes designed for different needs. So, there\'s the tiny E2B and E4B models which are only 2 billion and 4 billion parameters. This is perfect for running'

[01:30] [scene:talk]
